Overview:

   Threats to the Savage Land come from outside and from within as Ka-Zar struggles
   to make sense of growing conflicts among his people. With a terrible famine
   raging across Pangea, Outsiders are making plans to return. The forests burn as
   Pangeans strike deals with terrestrial corporations. And complicating this, the
   re-emergence of an ancient threat: the mysterious Ether Tribe have returned to
   punish anyone who dares deal with the outside world. Standing at the center of
   these myriad conflicts: one man and his tiger...



Contains:

   Ka-Zar 01-05 (of 05) (2011) (Minutemen)
